# UAE Logistics Dashboard (Power BI)

Power BI logistics dashboard project focused on shipment performance, delivery monitoring, and operational KPI reporting.

## Project Overview
This project presents a logistics operations dashboard for UAE shipment and transport performance analysis. It is designed to support operational monitoring and decision-making through clear KPI reporting and visual analytics.

## Key Business Questions
- What is the on-time delivery rate?
- Which routes or shipment types have the highest delay rate?
- How do shipment costs vary across transport modes?
- What operational trends affect logistics performance?

## Metrics Tracked
- Shipment volume
- Delay rate
- On-time delivery rate
- Average delivery duration
- Shipment cost
- Cost per km
- Route performance
- Transport mode performance

## Tools Used
- Power BI
- Data modeling
- DAX
- Logistics KPI reporting

## Project Value
This dashboard helps logistics teams monitor operations, identify delays, evaluate transport efficiency, and improve reporting for supply chain decision-making.
